review.reviewBody: Everything was delicious.  Chicken was tender. Prata is store bought but gravy is good .  One star off as sauces aren't good at all .   Wish they had actual ginger scallion sauce and the chilli sauce was spicy and more than bottles sweet chilli chicken sauce . Still their HCR is better than most places in Vancouver.

We really enjoyed the satay and the laksa was pretty decent too but I gotta say, as a Malaysian I gotta say the rendang is very much not what I know as rendang. My Irish husband called it a yummy stew
Delicious amazing fried rice and fried rice noodles and satay
smaller portion that I was hoping for but still tasty
Always our favorite Hainanese takeout place. large servings, juicy chicken, yum!
